template<unsigned ELEMENT_DIM, unsigned SPACE_DIM>
class VtkMeshReader< ELEMENT_DIM, SPACE_DIM >

VtkMeshReader

Reads a mesh (and data) from VTK .vtu format (that's an XML-based, data compressed unstructured mesh)
